PASSIVE: Spirit of the Stalker
	This unit has the Spirit of the Stalker imbued into them. Upon dealing damage, this unit deals 5 bonus true damage, heals 3 health, gains 2 experience, and gains one Stalker charge. Each charge increases the true damage and heal by one. This unit can have up to 3 Stalker charges, and charges disappear after one turn of not attacking. This passive has a one-turn cooldown.
